Table 1: IoU results on the Semantic-Kitti dataset test split. FPS measurements were taken using a single GTX 2080Ti 
GPU, or approximated if a runtime comparison was made on another GPU. Note that a FPS of 10 or more is considered 
real-time, since the acquisition frequency of the Velodyne HDL-64E 64 beam LiDAR sensor is 10 Hz.
